<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٣٦٤ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3651">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ رَجَاءٍ، </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/611">إِسْرَائِيلُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">الْبَرَاءِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«آخِرُ سُورَةٍ نَزَلَتْ كَامِلَةً بَرَاءَةٌ،<span class="c5"> وَآخِرُ سُورَةٍ نَزَلَتْ خَاتِمَةُ سُورَةِ النِّسَاءِ:</span> ﴿يَسْتَفْتُونَكَ قُلِ اللهُ يُفْتِيكُمْ فِي الْكَلالَةِ﴾»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>